<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PaLTM3.2.1">
<l>añcaṉa vaṇṇaṉai yāyar kulakkoḻun tiṉai</l>
<l>mañcaṉa māṭṭi maṉaikaḷtō ṟumtiri yāmē</l>
<l>kañcaṉaik kāynta kaḻalaṭi nōvakkaṉ ṟiṉpiṉ</l>
<l>eṉceyap piḷḷaiyaip pōkkiṉē ṉellēpā vamē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>After performing ablutions</l>
<l rend="indent">for the tender sprout of the herder lineage, the kohl-hued one,</l>
<l>why did I send [my] child after the calves</l>
<l rend="indent">to stop him from wandering in each of the houses?</l>
<l>[Now] the ankleted feet that tormented Kaṃsa ache.</l>
<l>Ah! What a sin!</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
